ges envoyés</div></div><div class=\"bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl p-3 cursor-pointer transition-all duration-200 hover:border-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-850 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg group\"><div class=\"text-lg font-bold text-emerald-400 mb-0.5 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110\">68%</div><div class=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-500 group-hover:text-zinc-400 transition-colors\">Taux de réponse</div></div><div class=\"bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl p-3 cursor-pointer transition-all duration-200 hover:border-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-850 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg group\"><div class=\"text-lg font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-0.5 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110\">347 k XAF</div><div class=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-500 group-hover:text-zinc-400 transition-colors\">Ventes générées</div></div></div><div class=\"space-y-1.5\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 sm:gap-3 bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl px-3 sm:px-4 py-2 sm:py-2.5 cursor-pointer group\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0 \"></div><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"text-xs font-medium text-white group-hover:text-green-400 transition-colors\">Promo Chaussures Yaoundé</div><div class=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-500 group-hover:text-zinc-400 transition-colors\">342 clients · photos produit</div></div><div class=\"text-[10px] font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full transition-all bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 group-hover:bg-green-500/20\">Envoyé</div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 sm:gap-3 bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl px-3 sm:px-4 py-2 sm:py-2.5 cursor-pointer group\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-500 shrink-0 animate-pulse\"></div><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"text-xs font-medium text-white group-hover:text-green-400 transition-colors\">Soldes Douala Nord</div><div class=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-500 group-hover:text-zinc-400 transition-colors\">215 clients · vidéo + prix</div></d