iv class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 cursor-pointer transition-all duration-200 hover:translate-x-1 group\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-lg bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5 group-hover:bg-zinc-750 transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-square h-3 w-3 text-blue-400 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110\"><path d=\"M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z\"></path></svg></div><div><div class=\"text-[11px] text-zinc-300 font-medium group-hover:text-white transition-colors\">Réponse IA : client</div><div class=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-600 group-hover:text-zinc-500 transition-colors\">Commande confirmée</div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 cursor-pointer transition-all duration-200 hover:translate-x-1 group\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-lg bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5 group-hover:bg-zinc-750 transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-activity h-3 w-3 text-purple-400 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110\"><path d=\"M22 12h-2.48a2 2 0 0 0-1.93 1.46l-2.35 8.36a.25.25 0 0 1-.48 0L9.24 2.18a.25.25 0 0 0-.48 0l-2.35 8.36A2 2 0 0 1 4.49 12H2\"></path></svg></div><div><div class=\"text-[11px] text-zinc-300 font-medium group-hover:text-white transition-colors\">Photo reçue par 215</div><div class=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-600 group-hover:text-zinc-500 transition-colors\">Soldes Douala Nord</div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 cursor-pointer transition-all duration-200 hover:translate-x-1 group\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-lg bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5 group-hover:bg-zinc-750 transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trending-up h-3 w-3 text-yellow-400 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110\"><polyline points=\"22 7 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 2 17\"></polyline><polyline points=\"16 7 22 7 22 13\"></polyline></svg></div><div><div class=\"text-[11px] text-zinc-300 font-medium group-hover:text-white transition-colors\">12 nouvelles ventes</div><div class=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-600 group-hover:text-zinc-500 transition-colors\">via WhatsApp</div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"absolute -bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-3/4 h-20 bg-green-500/20 blur-3xl rounded-full -z-10\"></div></div></div></section><section id=\"problems\" class=\"pt-20 sm:pt-28 pb-20 bg-black\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-8\"><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-end justify-between mb-10 sm:mb-12 gap-4\"><div class=\"max-w-xl\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-green-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3\">Le défi</p><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white leading-tight\">Ce qui freine vos ventes<br/>WhatsApp aujourd&#x27;hui</h2></div><a class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-zinc-400 hover:text-white transition-colors shrink-0 mb-1\" href=\"/#features\">Notre solution <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 overflow-hidden hover:border-zinc-700 transition-colors\"><div class=\"p-5 pb-0\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold text-zinc-400\">1</div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-white\">Envoi manuel, client par client</h3></div><p class=\"text-xs text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed mb-4\">Vous passez des heures à envoyer les mêmes photos produits et promotions un par un à chaque client. C&#x27;est lent, épuisant et non scalable.</p><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 p-3 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"space-y-2\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-zinc-700 flex items-center justify-center text-[9px] text-zinc-400 font-bold shrink-0\">K</div><span class=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-500 flex-1\">Konan A.<!-- --> — envoi manuel</span><span class=\"text-[9px] text-zinc-600\">2 min ago</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-zinc-700 flex items-center justify-center text-[9px] text-zinc-400 font-bold shrink-0\">B</div><span class=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-500 flex-1\">Brice M.<!-- --> — envoi manuel</span><span class=\"text-[9px] text-zinc-600\">5 min ago</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-zinc-700 flex items-center justify-center text-[9px] text-zinc-400 font-bold shrink-0\">D</div><span class=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-500 flex-1\">Diane K.<!-- --> — envoi manuel</span><span class=\"text-[9px] text-zinc-600\">8 min ago</span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"p-5\"><div class=\"text-xs font-medium text-green-500\">Envoi groupé à des centaines en 1 clic</div></div></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-green-500/30 bg-zinc-950 overflow-hidden shadow-lg shadow-green-500/5\"><div class=\"p-5 pb-0\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold text-green-400\">2</div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-white\">Aucune segmentation clientèle</h3></div><p class=\"text-xs text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed mb-4\">Vous envoyez le même message à tout le monde sans cibler par ville, par produit intérêt ou historique d&#x27;achat. Résultat : faible taux de conversion.</p><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 p-3\"><div class=\"space-y-1.5\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-500\">Filtre ville</span><span class=\"text-[10px] text-red-400\">non actif</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-500\">Filtre produit</span><span class=\"text-[10px] text-red-400\">non actif</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-500\">Segment acheteurs</span><span class=\"text-[10px] text-red-400\">non actif</span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"p-5\"><div class=\"text-xs font-medium text-green-500\">Ciblage précis par ville, produit, profil</div></div></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 overflow-hidden hover:border-zinc-700 transition-colors\"><div class=\"p-5 pb-0\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold text-zinc-400\">3</div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-white\">Réponses tardives = ventes perdues</h3></div><p class=\"text-xs text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed mb-4\">Un client qui ne reçoit pas de réponse dans les 5 minutes achète ailleurs. Vous ne pouvez pas répondre à tous en même temps manuellement.</p><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 p-3\"><div class=\"space-y-2\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><div class=\"w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-zinc-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5\"></div><div class=\"bg-zinc-800 rounded-lg px-2.5 py-1.5 text-[10px] text-zinc-400\">Le prix du sac svp ?</div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 justify-end\"><div class=\"bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 rounded-lg px-2.5 py-1.5 text-[10px] text-red-400\">Pas de réponse... 3h plus tard</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"p-5\"><div class=\"text-xs font-medium text-green-500\">Agent IA qui répond instantanément 24/7</div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"features\" class=\"py-16 sm:py-20 bg-zinc-950/50\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-14\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-green-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3\">Fonctionnalités</p><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4\">Tout ce qu&#x27;il vous faut pour vendre via WhatsApp</h2><p class=\"text-sm text-zinc-400 max-w-xl mx-auto\">Une plateforme taille pour les e-commerçants sérieux : diffusion en masse, ciblage précis, IA intégrée et médias riches.</p></div><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 overflow-hidden flex flex-col hover:border-zinc-700 transition-colors\"><div class=\"bg-zinc-900 border-b border-zinc-800 p-5\"><div class=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-3\">Nouvelle diffusion · Filtre actif</div><div class=\"space-y-2 mb-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between bg-zinc-800/50 rounded-lg px-3 py-1.5\"><span class=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-500\">Ville</span><span class=\"text-[10px] text-green-400 font-medium\">Yaoundé, Douala</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between bg-zinc-800/50 rounded-lg px-3 py-1.5\"><span class=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-500\">Produit</span><span class=\"text-[10px] text-green-400 font-medium\">Chaussures femme</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between bg-zinc-800/50 rounded-lg px-3 py-1.5\"><span class=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-500\">Clients cibles</span><span class=\"text-[10px] text-green-400 font-medium\">342 contacts</span></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 bg-zinc-800 rounded-lg px-3 py-2\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-zinc-700 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\"><span class=\"text-[9px] text-zinc-400\">IMG</span></div><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-300\">Promo chaussures -30% — photo.jpg</div><div class=\"text-[9px] text-zinc-600\">Prêt à envoyer à 342 clients</div></div><div class=\"text-[9px] text-green-400 bg-green-500/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded shrink-0\">Envoyer</div></div></div><div class=\"p-5 flex flex-col flex-1\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-green-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-send h-5 w-5 text-green-500\"><path d=\"M14.536 21.686a.5.5 0 0 0 .937-.024l6.5-19a.496.496 0 0 0-.635-.635l-19 6.5a.5.5 0 0 0-.024.937l7.93 3.18a2 2 0 0 1 1.112 1.11z\"></path><path d=\"m21.854 2.147-10.94 10.939\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2\">Diffusion ciblée en masse</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed flex-1\">Envoyez photos, vidéos, messages vocaux et promotions à des centaines de clients filtrés par ville, produit ou historique d&#x27;achat.</p><a class=\"mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-green-500 hover:text-green-400 transition-colors\" href=\"/register\">Démarrer <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-3.5 w-3.5\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-green-500/20 bg-zinc-950 overflow-hidden flex flex-col shadow-lg shadow-green-500/5\"><div class=\"bg-zinc-900 border-b border-zinc-800 p-5\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\"><div class=\"w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-green-500/20 flex items-center justify-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles h-3 w-3 text-green-400\"><path d=\"M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z\"></path><path d=\"M20 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 5h-4\"></path><path d=\"M4 17v2\"></path><path d=\"M5 18H3\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-[10px] text-green-400 font-medium\">Agent IA · en ligne</span></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><div class=\"w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-zinc-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5\"></div><div class=\"bg-zinc-800 rounded-xl rounded-tl-sm px-3 py-2 text-[10px] text-zinc-300\">C&#x27;est combien la robe rouge ?</div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 justify-end\"><div class=\"bg-green-600/20 border border-green-500/20 rounded-xl rounded-tr-sm px-3 py-2 text-[10px] text-green-300\">La robe rouge est à 12 500 XAF. Livraison disponible à Douala et Yaoundé. Vous voulez commander ?</div><div class=\"w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-green-600/20 shrink-0 mt-0.5 flex items-center justify-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles h-2.5 w-2.5 text-green-400\"><path d=\"M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z\"></path><path d=\"M20 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 5h-4\"></path><path d=\"M4 17v2\"></path><path d=\"M5 18H3\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><div class=\"w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-zinc-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5\"></div><div class=\"bg-zinc-800 rounded-xl rounded-tl-sm px-3 py-2 text-[10px] text-zinc-300\">Oui, taille M svp</div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 justify-end\"><div class=\"bg-green-600/20 border border-green-500/20 rounded-xl rounded-tr-sm px-3 py-2 text-[10px] text-green-300\">Parfait ! Je note votre commande. Quel est votre adresse de livraison ?</div><div class=\"w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-green-600/20 shrink-0 mt-0.5 flex items-center justify-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles h-2.5 w-2.5 text-green-400\"><path d=\"M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z\"></path><path d=\"M20 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 5h-4\"></path><path d=\"M4 17v2\"></path><path d=\"M5 18H3\"></path></svg></div></div></div></div><div class=\"p-5 flex flex-col flex-1\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-green-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles h-5 w-5 text-green-500\"><path d=\"M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z\"></path><path d=\"M20 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 5h-4\"></path><path d=\"M4 17v2\"></path><path d=\"M5 18H3\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2\">Agent IA qui vend à votre place</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed flex-1\">Configurez votre agent IA avec vos produits, prix et politiques. Il répond aux clients 24h/24, gère les commandes et ne laisse jamais une question sans réponse.</p><a class=\"mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-green-500 hover:text-green-400 transition-colors\" href=\"/register\">Configurer mon agent <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-3.5 w-3.5\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 overflow-hidden flex flex-col hover:border-zinc-700 transition-colors\"><div class=\"bg-zinc-900 border-b border-zinc-800 p-5\"><div class=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-3\">Types de médias supportés</div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 bg-zinc-800/50 rounded-lg px-2.5 py-2\"><span class=\"text-sm\">🖼️</span><span class=\"text-[10px] font-medium text-blue-300\">Photos produits</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 bg-zinc-800/50 rounded-lg px-2.5 py-2\"><span class=\"text-sm\">🎥</span><span class=\"text-[10px] font-medium text-purple-300\">Vidéos produits</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 bg-zinc-800/50 rounded-lg px-2.5 py-2\"><span class=\"text-sm\">🎤</span><span class=\"text-[10px] font-medium text-orange-300\">Messages vocaux</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 bg-zinc-800/50 rounded-lg px-2.5 py-2\"><span class=\"text-sm\">📄</span><span class=\"text-[10px] font-medium text-red-300\">Catalogues PDF</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 bg-zinc-800/50 rounded-lg px-2.5 py-2\"><span class=\"text-sm\">📍</span><span class=\"text-[10px] font-medium text-yellow-300\">Localisation</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 bg-zinc-800/50 rounded-lg px-2.5 py-2\"><span class=\"text-sm\">📞</span><span class=\"text-[10px] font-medium text-green-300\">Contacts partagés</span></div></div></div><div class=\"p-5 flex flex-col flex-1\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-green-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-activity h-5 w-5 text-green-500\"><path d=\"M22 12h-2.48a2 2 0 0 0-1.93 1.46l-2.35 8.36a.25.25 0 0 1-.48 0L9.24 2.18a.25.25 0 0 0-.48 0l-2.35 8.36A2 2 0 0 1 4.49 12H2\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2\">Médias riches à grande échelle</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed flex-1\">Envoyez photos de produits, vidéos de présentation, bons de réduction en PDF et messages vocaux personnalisés à tous vos clients simultanément.</p><a class=\"mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-green-500 hover:text-green-400 transition-colors\" href=\"/register\">Démarrer <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-3.5 w-3.5\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"integration\" class=\"py-16 sm:py-20 bg-black\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-8 text-center\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-green-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3\">Intégrations</p><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4\">Connecte-toi à tes outils e-commerce</h2><p class=\"text-sm text-zinc-400 max-w-lg mx-auto mb-12\">Synchronise ta boutique, importe ta liste clients et automatise tes envois directement depuis tes outils existants.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 sm:grid-cols-4 md:grid-cols-6 gap-3 sm:gap-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-2 p-4 rounded-xl bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 hover:border-zinc-700 transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trending-up h-6 w-6 text-green-400\"><polyline points=\"22 7 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 2 17\"></polyline><polyline points=\"16 7 22 7 22 13\"></polyline></svg><span class=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-500 font-medium\">Shopify</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-2 p-4 rounded-xl bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 hover:border-zinc-700 transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe h-6 w-6 text-blue-400\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-500 font-medium\">WooCommerce</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-2 p-4 rounded-xl bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 hover:border-zinc-700 transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chart-column h-6 w-6 text-emerald-40